{"tid":953905,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"後生仔齊支持港航 不擔心無港航航班回港 「要執(倒閉)都一段時間先執」","createTime":"2018-12-24T09:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T09:22:52.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2be86e5c25c2a01599282a43097e77c159a6fcb5","tid":953905,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T09:22:52.000Z","msg":"謝先生表示，選乘香港航空去北京再轉飛英國，預期在英國逗留一個月，回程機票亦是選擇香港航空，雖然近日盛傳香港航空陷財務危機，但謝先生表示不擔心，因為「冇遇過」，如果萬一香港航空真的因為財困而倒閉，最多回港時「買過張機票，冇辦法」。 <br />\n<br />\n黎先生則買了香港航空的來回機票，到台灣旅遊至月底，他亦對事件表示不擔心，「要執(倒閉)都一段時間先執」。黎先生有購買旅遊保險，但「冇留意保險細節」，不知道萬一香港航空真的出現問題，無法提供回程航班時，會否獲得賠償，但最多亦是「焗住會買過一張」。 <br />\n<br />\n鄭小姐偕母親到台灣旅遊，下個月19日才回港，來回機票都買了香港航空，她們亦表示不太擔心，萬一有事就「買過張機票回港」，又指若香港航空安然渡過危機，日後仍會繼續選搭。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181224/59065321?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_web&amp;itm_content=internal_link_2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181224%2F59065321%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_web%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_2&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=ec530ee3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181224%2F59065321%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_web%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_2&h=1a874981\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181224/59065321?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_web&amp;itm_content=internal_link_2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181224/large/1545632055_ecfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181224%2Flarge%2F1545632055_ecfb.jpg&h=f865fc54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝先生表示不擔心，因為「冇遇過」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181224/large/1545632055_b4e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181224%2Flarge%2F1545632055_b4e4.jpg&h=2052b262&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎先生對事件表示不擔心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181224/small/1545632773_9998.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181224%2Fsmall%2F1545632773_9998.jpg&h=34816dac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萬一有事就「買過張機票回港」，又指若香港航空安然渡過危機，日後仍會繼續選搭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登仔太年輕了樣樣怕"}]}